data.title: Data by region
data.text:
Information about Data by region

For more information about the statistics view Data by region methodology.

Search by map or region list to find statistics about different areas in Australia.

Data by region is intended for users interested in the characteristics of regions and for comparing regions across Australia.

Data are available for Local Government Areas, Remoteness Areas, Indigenous Structure levels, Statistical Areas Levels 2 - 4, Greater Capital City Statistical Areas, states, territories and Australia covering various topics (including population, economy, industry, income, employment, education and health).

For more information about the statistics view Data by region methodology.
